  <brief_title>Evaluation Study of a Mouthwash Based on Schinus Terebinthifolius to Treat Gingivitis in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Evaluation of a Mouthwash Based on Schinus Terebinthifolius (Aroeira) Used by Children With Gingivitis</official_title>
